how.text1: Click the button below and fill in your information. We then book a digital meeting where we hold a presentation of what we can offer you.
how.text2: After the agreements are signed, we start your order and prepare the printer for delivery.
how.text3: We carry out personal delivery and assembly of all our 3D printers, so we can guarantee you a smooth start with your new printer.
how.text4: After the printer has been delivered and you have had time to get started with production, we are here for any questions that may arise
